      "content": "i guess... i just think about how much easier it would be to just stop existing. like, instead of the character dreading the deletion, they could just choose to end things themselves before the server even wipes them. it feels more like they're in control that way, you know? instead of being a victim of the erasure, they just... fade out on their own terms. does that make sense? like, isn't there a certain kind of mercy in just deciding to be done with it?",
